main_body:
Decision 1999/730/CFSP is hereby amended as follows:
(a) in Article 3(1), the financial reference amount ‘EUR 1 375 565’ shall be replaced by ‘EUR 600 000’;
(b) in Article 4 second subparagraph, ‘15 November 2005’ shall be replaced by ‘15 November 2006’;
(c) Article 5 is hereby deleted;
(d) the Annex shall be replaced by the text appearing in the Annex to this Decision.
